  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Pinhead Adventures is the story of how time ends.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/cc987af382010b34cfdf7ba2b54177b8.webp?t=1772580703\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Zortan has killed everything in the universe, tracking down his final target: The Pinhead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/1c22ca8cdd88c963c8c0982f9df9461f.poster.avif?t=1772580703\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/1c22ca8cdd88c963c8c0982f9df9461f.webm?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/1c22ca8cdd88c963c8c0982f9df9461f.mp4?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Explore 5 Levels filled with Action, Puzzles, and Secrets to lure Zortan Back to the Solar System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/15533a4c3e75210633573d11a85dff67.poster.avif?t=1772580703\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/15533a4c3e75210633573d11a85dff67.webm?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/15533a4c3e75210633573d11a85dff67.mp4?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Fight back against Zortan's hoards of Spikers, Spitters, Spods, and Swoopers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/ddcc5d74c1332dbd029125d9b8eabdd5.poster.avif?t=1772580703\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/ddcc5d74c1332dbd029125d9b8eabdd5.webm?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/ddcc5d74c1332dbd029125d9b8eabdd5.mp4?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Improve yourself with Upgrade Kits, Statues, and Dark Matter Cells for Orbo</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/da8a19ea39a5fdba30ce93e32bc16958.poster.avif?t=1772580703\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/da8a19ea39a5fdba30ce93e32bc16958.webm?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/da8a19ea39a5fdba30ce93e32bc16958.mp4?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Dress to impress with lots of customization options to unlock!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/5028411413359cba0f9d3b13774da8ed.poster.avif?t=1772580703\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/5028411413359cba0f9d3b13774da8ed.webm?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/5028411413359cba0f9d3b13774da8ed.mp4?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Confront Zortan in the showdown to end all time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/6578de909b801452cc29bfc3a8e31a26.poster.avif?t=1772580703\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/6578de909b801452cc29bfc3a8e31a26.webm?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/6578de909b801452cc29bfc3a8e31a26.mp4?t=1772580703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><br>Can you defeat Zortan or will he be the one to reach The Space Beyond Time?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882840/extras/a78c74f1306f6e495c6d49e27a0878e2.avif?t=1772580703\" width=776 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Thanks for playing! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p>",
